php -v
composer -V

Composer:
composer require --dev phpstan/phpstan
vendor\bin\phpstan analyse test.php  

parameters:
	level: 6
	paths:
		- test.php
		- test2.php

        
Level 0: Basic checks (unknown classes/functions/methods, wrong args, undefined vars)
Level 1: Possibly undefined vars, unknown magic methods/properties
Level 2: Unknown methods on all expressions, PHPDoc validation
Level 3: Return types, property types
Level 4: Dead code (unreachable code, false instanceof)
Level 5: Argument types check
Level 6: Missing typehints report
Level 7: Union types issues (e.g., method exists on some types only)
Level 8: Nullable types methods/properties call
Level 9: Strict mixed type (explicit mixed)
Level 10: Even stricter mixed (implicit mixed, missing types)



baseline:
vendor/bin/phpstan analyse test2.php -l 10
vendor/bin/phpstan analyse test2.php -l 10 --generate-baseline baseline.neon

includes:
	- baseline.neon

vendor/bin/phpstan analyse test2.php -l 10

Format:
Table: vendor\bin\phpstan analyse 
Raw: vendor\bin\phpstan analyse --error-format=raw
Checkstyle: vendor\bin\phpstan analyse --error-format=checkstyle > checkstyle.xml
JSON: vendor\bin\phpstan analyse --error-format=json > output.json
JUnit: vendor\bin\phpstan analyse --error-format=junit > junit.xml
GitHub: vendor\bin\phpstan analyse --error-format=github

